10:
Stop! It's impossible to break the Circle 
now—you'll only hurt yourself!
28:
I AM INAHO TAMAMO!
DAUGHTER OF THE NINE-TAILED FOX!
Your dumb barrier is NOTHING before 
MY power!
32:
You don't need to do this to yourself! 
Why are you going to such lengths to 
spare me?!
35:
Long ago, Soushiro saved me! Now it is 
my turn to be a hero!
Shut up and let me save you!
38:
Have you already forgotten what I did 
to you?!
42:
I have not forgotten...
I have FORGIVEN!
46:
The... the Circle...
But, but how?
51:
Just when things were getting good. 
I was rather looking forward to a taste 
of Izumi's power.
55:
Oh well! All will be One in the end 
anyhow.
61: We made it in time, Shirano.
65:
Princess! Oh goodness, I'm so glad 
you're okay! Don't scare me like that!
73:
Why! Why did you spare me?! 
The Circle of Corros—
79:
Suizen, stop. Take a deep breath and 
think about what you just tried to do. 
You would have died, leaving behind 
nothing but a near unbreakable ring of 
destruction.
81:
You are young, and have much to live 
for—things you wish to do, things you 
MUST do.
Think. Think of what those are.
84:
Now then, the rest of us have a serpent 
to slay!
89:
Yeah, with all of us working together, 
I'm sure we can defeat it!
94:
Who cares if it's super powerful or 
whatever! So are we!
98:
Not the smartest bunch, are they? You 
fools just squandered your only hope 
of victory!
100:
Go, Orochi. Devour them! The stars! 
Every last glimmer of light!
...NOW!
